      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the legendary S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers razor-sharp throttle response via six individual throttle bodies, with the high-pressure VANOS system operating flawlessly across the entire 8,000 RPM sweep. Power is managed through a precise ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension geometry that remains factory-spec tight. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle displays no aesthetic or mechanical degradation, representing the pinnacle of the E46's analog driving dynamics.",
